    <item>
      <title>Docs: Input source color configuration</title>
      <link>/docs/configuration/color-configuration/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/configuration/color-configuration/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;You can change indicator colors of input sources.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../open-preferences-window/&#34;&gt;Open preferences window&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Press &lt;code&gt;Add custom color&lt;/code&gt; button on Preferences.
&lt;figure&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;/images/add-color.png&#34;/&gt; 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Change colors.
&lt;figure&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;/images/change-color.png&#34;/&gt; 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Docs: Indicator size configuration</title>
      <link>/docs/configuration/indicator-size-configuration/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/configuration/indicator-size-configuration/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        

&lt;h2 id=&#34;basic&#34;&gt;Basic&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can change the indicator height.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../open-preferences-window/&#34;&gt;Open preferences window&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Adjust height.
&lt;figure&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;/images/indicator-height.png&#34;/&gt; 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;advanced&#34;&gt;Advanced&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can put the indicator by custom size and origin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../open-preferences-window/&#34;&gt;Open preferences window&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open &lt;code&gt;Advanced&lt;/code&gt; tab, then enable &lt;code&gt;Use custom frame&lt;/code&gt;.
&lt;figure&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;/images/indicator-size.png&#34;/&gt; 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Docs: Resume configuration</title>
      <link>/docs/configuration/resume-configuration/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/docs/configuration/resume-configuration/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;ShowyEdge will be automatically started at login by default.&lt;br&gt;
Follow instructions if you want to disable the feature.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;../open-preferences-window/&#34;&gt;Open preferences window&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open &lt;code&gt;Advanced&lt;/code&gt; tab, then enable &lt;code&gt;Resume at login&lt;/code&gt;.
&lt;figure&gt;
    &lt;img src=&#34;/images/resume-at-login.png&#34;/&gt; 
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
